<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>CFB Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #001f3f;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #003366;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #008000;
    }
    .info {
      background-color: #001f3f;
      color: white;
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    .info p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .info p span.min {
      color: #008000;
    }
    .info p span.max {
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .start-btn {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      background-color: #004080;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .start-btn:hover {
      background-color: #0059b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Invest in CFB Company</h1>
  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Trust and Invest CFB and Become Future Billionaire</h1>
    <h2>But you have to first invest in CFB</h2>

    <div class="info">
      <p>Minimum Investing Amount: <span class="min">$50</span></p>
      <p>Maximum Investing Amount: <span class="max">$10,000</span></p>
      <p>For Investing Contact Us</p>
    </div>

    <button class="start-btn" onclick="alert('Contact us to start investing!')">START</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
